This directory contains tools used in maintaining this package.
Specifically:

README
    This file.

events
    Run one of the Test2::Tools::LoadModule subroutines and dump the
    events generated. The name of the subroutine and the module to load
    are specified as command arguments. The rest of the possible
    subroutine arguments are specified as options.

version_regex
    Builds the LAX_VERSION constant in Test2::Tools::LoadModule from
    $version::regex::LAX. Use with caution, since version::regex is
    completely undocumented.

